{"tid":976371,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯外儲組合大調整！美元佔比急降至22%　人民幣暴增至15%","createTime":"2019-01-10T11:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T01:07:21.000Z","uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3168476d7cde7b284e78a56b10fc3f78e888a3b2","tid":976371,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190110/photo/bkn-20190110091822733-0110_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190110121337\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190110%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190110091822733-0110_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190110121337&h=faf46b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據俄羅斯央行周三公布數據，截至2018年6月30日，該央行將美元在儲備中的比例，從1年前的46%降低到22%。<br />\n<br />\n至於歐元所佔比則從2017年6月底的25%上升至32%；人民幣佔比從1年前的0.1%上漲至15%。<br />\n<br />\n外國政府債券佔比從1年前的52%降至40%，銀行存款從19%上升到29%。"},{"pid":"17632c4f4803aa376f6dfef816704d49756ff944","tid":976371,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:08:49.000Z","msg":"聽日又大爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e4c5660f138b435223d1550fc15bbd2f908a24","tid":976371,"uid":27150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:09:43.000Z","msg":"多邊落注"},{"pid":"fffe5dde044f55830deef7fad2bdde9ebf9fb46a","tid":976371,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:09:44.000Z","msg":"話比人聽盧布係廢紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea93405936d5e8ca507614287b2e51b2f512706","tid":976371,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"唔怪得cny 升"},{"pid":"e22965ca201aa0d6da9402e348d91d6cae77e5e8","tid":976371,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"點解會有人儲陰司紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa344cac43273ae5f711f1d4c95fd